<v HOST_1>It sounds almost too good to be true. But for all its brilliance, a powerful tool can also be a dangerous one...HOST_2: enthusiastic A huge impact, Sarah, and in ways that go far beyond just writing code snippets. Its about accelerating entire development cycles and solving problems that were previously massive headaches.

